'''蛏蚌属'''（学名：{{lang|la|''Solenaia''}}）为[[蚌目|蚌目]][[蚌科|蚌科]][[隆嵴蚌亚科|隆嵴蚌亚科]]一個[[淡水动物|淡水动物]]的[[属_(生物)|属]]。

==物種==
目前在[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]只記載有[[三角蛏蚌|三角蛏蚌]]一個物種<ref name=WoRMS_747103>{{cite WoRMS |title=''Solenaia'' Conrad, 1869 |id=747103 |accessdate=2015-04-09 |date=2014-01-25 |last=Bouchet |first=Philippe }}</ref>，但在華文的文獻，本屬至少有五個物種<ref name=cnki>{{cite journal |url=http://wap.cnki.net/lunwen-1012290873.html |title=中国蚌科动物的分子系统进化及遗传多样性研究 |author=欧阳解秀 |accessdate=2015-04-09 |language=zh-hans |journal=南昌大学博士论文 |publisher=[[南昌大学|南昌大学]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202042005/http://wap.cnki.net/lunwen-1012290873.html |archive-date=2017-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而在[[美國|美國]][[威斯康辛州大學斯提芬斯岬分校|威斯康辛州大學斯提芬斯岬分校]]的[[MusselP數據庫|MusselP數據庫]]裡記載有八個物種<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mussel-project.uwsp.edu/db/db.php?p=div&l=gen&n=106 |title=''Solenaia'' Conrad, 1869: species |publisher=[[MusselP數據庫|MusselP數據庫]] |language=en |accessdate=2015-04-09 |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012095929/http://mussel-project.uwsp.edu/db/db.php?p=div&l=gen&n=106 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。綜合上述各文獻，本屬物種如下：
*[[龙骨蛏蚌|龙骨蛏蚌]] ''Solenaia carinata'' (Heude, 1877)<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.cqvip.com/QK/90158X/199101/474298.html |title=龙骨蛏蚌的再描述（真瓣鳃目：蚌科） |journal=《[[动物分类学报|动物分类学报]]》 |year=1991 |issue=第1期 |author1=[[刘月英|刘月英]] |author2=[[吴小平|吴小平]] |language=zh-hans |author= |access-date=2015-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019111524/http://www.cqvip.com/QK/90158X/199101/474298.html |archive-date=2017-10-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>：見於[[中國|中國]][[長江|長江]]沿岸。
* ''Solenaia emarginata'' (Lea, 1860)：見於中國長江沿岸。
*[[桂河蛏蚌|桂河蛏蚌]] ''Solenaia khwaenoiensis'' Panha & Deein, 2003：以發現地、[[泰國|泰國]][[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]著名戰場[[桂河大桥_(电影)|桂河]]命名。發現後再沒有紀錄，資料不齊全。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/171807/0 |title=''Solenaia khwaenoiensis'' |work=[[IUCN_Red_List_of_Threatened_Species|IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] |edition=2014.3 |language=en |accessdate=2015-04-09 |archive-date=2018-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602111545/http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/171807/0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*[[橄榄蛏蚌|橄榄蛏蚌]] ''Solenaia iridinea'' (Heude, 1874)：見於中國長江沿岸。
*[[新三角蛏蚌|新三角蛏蚌]] ''Solenaia neotriangularis'' He & Zhuang, 2013<ref name=WoRMS_747104>{{cite WoRMS |title=''Solenaia neotriangularis'' He & Zhuang, 2013  |id=747104 |accessdate=2015-04-09 |date=2014-01-25 |last=Bouchet |first=Philippe }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=He |first1=Jiang |last2=Zhuang |first2=Zimin |year=2013 |title=The freshwater bivalves of China. |publisher=Harxheim: Conchbooks. |pages=197 pp. }}</ref>：見於中國長江沿岸。
*[[河蛏蚌|河蛏蚌]] ''Solenaia rivularis'' (Heude, 1877)：見於中國長江沿岸。
*''Solenaia soleniformis'' (Benson, 1836)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/166770/0 |title=''Solenaia soleniformis'' |work=[[IUCN_Red_List_of_Threatened_Species|IUCN Red List of Threatened Species]] |edition=2014.3 |language=en |accessdate=2015-04-09 |archive-date=2018-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602204251/http://www.iucnredlist.org/details/166770/0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>：見於[[印度東北部|印度東北部]]。
*[[三角蛏蚌|三角蛏蚌]] ''Solenaia triangularis'' (Heude, 1885)：見於中國[[四川省|四川省]]長江上游及[[大韓民國|大韓民國]]。

